Adaptive Traffic Light Simulator
--------------------------------
Enter number of cycles to simulate (e.g., 3): 1
Choose input mode: 1) Manual densities  2) Random densities
Enter 1 or 2: 1
Run in real-time (sleep between phases)? 1=Yes 0=No (choose 0 for fast output): 0
Enter NS (North-South) traffic density (non-negative integer): 80
Enter EW (East-West) traffic density (non-negative integer): 20
